{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, of course, when I had my own family, that was a very happy time for her, when I had my own children, and she had her grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was a very happy time for her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just that I had told a rabbi about it and, you know, saying Kaddish, and-- but--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was too much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was her mother had been killed and her sisters had been killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and she just couldn't, you know-- she couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to-- again, I worked in a-- in an art studio.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then at night, I began to go to Pratt to get my degree.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in those days, they did not give a full degree if you went-- went at night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in 1979, I went back after-- while I was running a big studio at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went in the evening and I got my degree a year later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was some family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was family here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And matter of fact, another aunt came here who had been in Romania doing the war, and her son and eventually daughter-in-law came.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And who else was here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her brother was here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was some family constellation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I was still somewhat involved with my father's brothers and their children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were invited to their affairs and so on, actually 'til my first wife died, and then I stopped that relationship.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't-- I haven't had any contact with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '49.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my wife was born-- Norma was born here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her family was born here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her father and mother were born here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I really didn't want to-- I didn't want to speak German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I almost never spoke German.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
